  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "XI JUMBO was released as a sequel to Devil Dice only released in Japan.\nThe rule is similar to its predecessor, but in this version, you can stack the dice vertically by lift up or jump with a die.\n\nThe classical \"Trial - Time Limited\" and \"Puzzle\" modes are also available on this version.\nFor new features, The \"Battle\" mode is entirely renewed with a garbage-attacking style.\nIn addition, a new task-solving trial, named \"Norma Attack,\" is introduced.",
